These words describe the size of message that a Speaker is judged by a (usually unexpressed) Judge to give, either in a specific occasion or Topic or in general. As in other communication frames, Medium may also be expressed.

big mouth.n, brusque.a, chatterbox.n, chatty.a, curt.a, effusive.a, expansive.a, garrulous.a, glib.a, gushing.a, gushy.a, laconic.a, loquacious.a, loquacity.n, loudmouth.n, mum.a, mute.a, quiet.a, reserved.a, reticence.n, reticent.a, silent.a, taciturn.a, talkative.a, terse.a, uncommunicative.a, voluble.a
